WEBVTT

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:27.830
For it reaches to the highest mountain.

00:00:30.040 --> 00:00:31.790
Those are communion cups

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:34.190
from the last couple times.

00:00:34.190 --> 00:00:34.200
I

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:34.870
have

00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:36.470
to start picking up my stuff a

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:39.070
little bit more.

00:00:39.080 --> 00:00:41.190
Oh, there it goes. All four.

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:43.110
Bummer.

00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:47.070
Is anybody here? Yeah.

00:00:51.720 --> 00:00:54.590
Father, I plead the blood of Jesus.

00:00:55.640 --> 00:00:57.030
Thank you, Father, for your angels

00:00:57.040 --> 00:01:01.510
that watch over us tonight as we pray.

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:03.430
Thank you, Father, that we only pray

00:01:03.430 --> 00:01:03.440
with

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:05.229
your heart,

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:08.630
no flesh. Thank you, Lord.

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:12.190
We go right into the throne,

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:15.190
Lord.

00:01:19.760 --> 00:01:26.510
Ready?

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:29.790
Good evening, family.

00:01:29.800 --> 00:01:31.710
How are y'all doing today? I

00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:35.870
just wanted to come on tonight and

00:01:35.880 --> 00:01:38.430
pray with you for a little bit.

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:40.430
Last night when we prayed, we prayed

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:42.910
really late to reach other parts of

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:45.350
the world, but my heart was to pray for

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:48.270
Australia. We prayed for Australia,

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:53.950
Africa, and New Zealand.

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:55.910
The Lord was showing us a great

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:58.590
revival coming to Australia, a fresh,

00:01:58.600 --> 00:02:00.830
new, mighty outpouring of the Spirit of

00:02:00.840 --> 00:02:04.670
God. Then I was seeing new songs;

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:06.310
new

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:09.109
heavenly songs are going to start to

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:10.550
come forth.

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:12.870
The Lord was telling us

00:02:12.880 --> 00:02:14.950
to pull on that.

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:17.590
If you are a person that

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:20.070
makes music and

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.950
writes music,

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:23.550
I believe there's going to be

00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:26.190
heavenly music given to you as you press

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:28.670
into the Father. You're not seeking

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:31.030
fame or finances,

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:34.030
but you're seeking just to worship.

00:02:34.040 --> 00:02:36.590
I believe the Lord

00:02:36.600 --> 00:02:38.670
doesn't care if we have blessings, as long

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:40.790
as the blessings don't have us.

00:02:40.800 --> 00:02:42.910
I want you to know that's

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:44.070
what the Lord was showing us: that there

00:02:44.070 --> 00:02:44.080
are

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:47.110
new heavenly songs coming. There

00:02:47.110 --> 00:02:47.120
are

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:49.190
songs that we've

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:50.790
never heard before that are

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:52.590
going to be

00:02:52.600 --> 00:02:55.750
glorious. Beautiful music is coming, and

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:58.430
I would expect it right now.

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:02.750
As we were praying last night, we saw

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:04.710
the power grid again.

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:09.910
As President Trump

00:03:09.920 --> 00:03:11.790
starts doing these tariffs and

00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:14.350
sanctions, the Lord

00:03:14.360 --> 00:03:16.990
showed me attacks against the

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:19.030
power grid:

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:21.750
Los Angeles, the Bay Area,

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:25.710
Chicago, and New York—these places of

00:03:25.720 --> 00:03:28.470
great populations. The Lord told us

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:31.270
last night we need to pray against power

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.630
outages

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:35.910
concerning cyber attacks and cyber

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:38.870
warfare.

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:40.750
I don't know who would be taking care of

00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:43.470
our power grid—maybe our army

00:03:43.470 --> 00:03:43.480
or

00:03:44.430 --> 00:03:44.440
whoever

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:45.750
is

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:48.030
over the cyber

00:03:48.030 --> 00:03:48.040
division—to

00:03:48.040 --> 00:03:50.790
have supernatural wisdom on how to

00:03:50.800 --> 00:03:54.550
combat the attacks that are coming.

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:56.750
I believe they've already started. I

00:03:56.760 --> 00:03:59.990
saw Trojan horses

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:03.590
coming in and causing disruption in our

00:04:03.600 --> 00:04:07.030
power grid in America in a greater way.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:09.430
It would not just be

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:14.030
a couple of hours of power outage; we're

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:17.229
talking a sustained amount of power

00:04:17.239 --> 00:04:20.190
being out for maybe days.

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:22.510
I'm not trying to stir up fear;

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:24.190
I'm trying to tell you it's something

00:04:24.200 --> 00:04:25.870
you should be prayerful about.

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:28.190
Every single thing I bring

00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:30.310
to you is to bring

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:33.110
prayer over our nation and for our

00:04:33.120 --> 00:04:35.310
president, for Homeland Security,

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:39.070
the FBI, and the CIA. I

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.590
just believe that there's power in

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:44.070
prayer. Just as we saw that the man in

00:04:44.080 --> 00:04:46.310
Atlanta was going to try to do a mass

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:49.310
shooting there and he was stopped by

00:04:49.320 --> 00:04:52.430
the authorities. All glory to God.

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:54.910
There was confusion in the camp,

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:57.190
and that's what we pray: that

00:04:57.200 --> 00:04:58.390
they don't have their thoughts right

00:04:58.400 --> 00:04:59.910
when they're trying to do things like

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:02.630
that. He went in and his

00:05:02.640 --> 00:05:04.910
family told on him, and then all of a

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:06.710
sudden the

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.190
authorities said they believed that he

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:10.670
was going back. He was scoping out the

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:13.190
area and going back to his truck

00:05:13.200 --> 00:05:14.710
to get whatever he was going to get

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:16.950
to hurt people.

00:05:16.950 --> 00:05:16.960
I

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:20.750
believe this is what we're called to do.

00:05:20.760 --> 00:05:22.270
We're

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:24.870
assembling together tonight to

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:28.710
stop Satan's plans.

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:30.430
Principalities work

00:05:30.440 --> 00:05:32.230
through personalities.

00:05:34.840 --> 00:05:36.870
Weak-minded people

00:05:36.870 --> 00:05:36.880
who

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:39.190
already have a reprobate mind

00:05:39.190 --> 00:05:39.200
and

00:05:39.200 --> 00:05:41.190
are not strong in the Word

00:05:41.190 --> 00:05:41.200
are

00:05:41.200 --> 00:05:42.190
coming in, and they're

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:43.990
trying to grab a hold of these people

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:45.590
that already have yielded

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:49.470
themselves over to demonic influence.

00:05:49.480 --> 00:05:52.270
We want to pray for a hedge of

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:54.310
protection around our sporting events, including

00:05:54.310 --> 00:05:54.320
the

00:05:54.320 --> 00:05:58.390
World Series that starts

00:05:58.390 --> 00:05:58.400
tomorrow,

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:00.590
Friday.

00:06:04.200 --> 00:06:06.190
We pray over

00:06:06.200 --> 00:06:08.270
the World Series;

00:06:08.280 --> 00:06:11.750
it's best out of seven.

00:06:11.750 --> 00:06:11.760
We

00:06:11.760 --> 00:06:13.390
are

00:06:13.400 --> 00:06:15.190
praying over our college events and any kind of major event: Thanksgiving,

00:06:15.190 --> 00:06:15.200
Black Friday, and all these things. We are

00:06:15.200 --> 00:06:18.110
praying over our

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:26.750
economy

00:06:26.750 --> 00:06:26.760
and

00:06:26.760 --> 00:06:28.990
for President Trump.

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:31.870
As he said, he's putting more sanctions

00:06:31.880 --> 00:06:34.470
on Russia and their oil

00:06:34.480 --> 00:06:35.830
companies,

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:36.990
so

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.390
we know what will happen with that. I

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:41.510
just believe this

00:06:41.510 --> 00:06:41.520
situation—you

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:44.910
try to put people in a corner

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:46.350
by touching their

00:06:46.350 --> 00:06:46.360
pocketbook—but

00:06:46.360 --> 00:06:48.990
I've seen an escalation

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:51.990
of things. I heard one pastor say,

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.390
'Oh, Brandon, we're going to stop war

00:06:54.390 --> 00:06:54.400
altogether.'Well,

00:06:54.400 --> 00:06:56.870
that goes against

00:06:56.880 --> 00:06:59.230
Matthew 24.

00:06:59.240 --> 00:07:00.870
I'm going to line up with

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:03.110
the Word, not with what you think.

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:05.710
The Bible said we would have wars

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:08.670
and rumors of wars.

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:13.190
We'll have plagues,

00:07:13.200 --> 00:07:14.870
pestilences,

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:16.750
and

00:07:16.760 --> 00:07:18.270
famines.

00:07:18.280 --> 00:07:20.270
This is the

00:07:20.280 --> 00:07:23.750
beginning of sorrows,

00:07:23.760 --> 00:07:26.430
and I believe we're in that

00:07:26.430 --> 00:07:26.440
timeframe.

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:28.790
No matter how much we try to stop

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:31.070
it,

00:07:31.080 --> 00:07:32.550
you're not

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:34.550
going to stop the Bible. The Bible

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:37.190
stands alone, and there is no prophetic

00:07:37.200 --> 00:07:39.190
word that's going to go against the Word

00:07:39.200 --> 00:07:41.310
of God. If it goes against the Word of

00:07:41.320 --> 00:07:43.350
God, it's not God and it's not

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:45.230
a prophetic word; it's a false word,

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:47.590
a false prophecy. We know

00:07:47.600 --> 00:07:49.670
what's coming, ladies and gentlemen.

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:52.150
The Lord said to me today while I was

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:54.510
outside,

00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:56.670
'Brandon, there's not enough

00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:58.310
urgency.

00:07:58.320 --> 00:08:00.670
Again, you must tell My people I'm

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:02.310
coming

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:04.750
again. You must tell them that they need

00:08:04.760 --> 00:08:08.310
to have a sense of urgency about My

00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:10.470
coming.'I

00:08:10.480 --> 00:08:12.710
went over what I said to you

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:14.950
all yesterday. Every time I

00:08:14.960 --> 00:08:17.390
go over

00:08:17.400 --> 00:08:19.110
everything I've said to

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:20.670
you

00:08:20.680 --> 00:08:22.270
because I don't want any prophetic

00:08:22.280 --> 00:08:23.550
confusion.

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:25.190
I've said a thousand

00:08:25.200 --> 00:08:26.670
times,

00:08:26.670 --> 00:08:26.680
and

00:08:26.680 --> 00:08:27.910
Paul Begley and others

00:08:27.920 --> 00:08:29.350
say, 'Brandon, you're called to

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:31.350
be like a prophet,'but I always say I'm

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:32.630
a watchman

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:34.990
and I believe I have a prophetic lens.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.870
I'm able to see, and the Lord said,

00:08:36.880 --> 00:08:39.430
'Your main focus is to bring prayer to

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:41.790
YouTube. I want you to bring a massive

00:08:41.800 --> 00:08:44.550
prayer audience. I want a million-man

00:08:44.550 --> 00:08:44.560
and woman

00:08:44.560 --> 00:08:48.270
prayer army. As you pray,

00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:49.910
you will change things and you will

00:08:49.920 --> 00:08:52.190
protect what's coming.'If they don't

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:55.590
know Psalm 91 and Psalm 23, they're in

00:08:55.600 --> 00:08:57.590
trouble.

00:08:57.590 --> 00:08:57.600
Is

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:59.270
that to scare you? No, it's to

00:08:59.280 --> 00:09:01.270
prepare you. You must know the Word of

00:09:01.280 --> 00:09:02.310
God.

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:05.470
You must understand your covenant.

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:07.350
I know there are a lot of Word of

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.350
Faith people who believe we're not

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:11.230
going to go through anything,

00:09:11.230 --> 00:09:11.240
saying,

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:12.750
'Well, brother,

00:09:12.760 --> 00:09:14.630
as long as we're the salt,

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:16.230
we're holding back the

00:09:16.230 --> 00:09:16.240
Antichrist.'I

00:09:16.240 --> 00:09:17.590
believe

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:19.270
wholeheartedly

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:21.830
that we are the salt and

00:09:21.840 --> 00:09:24.190
the restrainer because the Holy Ghost is

00:09:24.200 --> 00:09:25.630
in us. Some people

00:09:25.640 --> 00:09:26.630
believe we're going to go through the

00:09:26.640 --> 00:09:29.270
whole tribulation. I do not.

00:09:29.280 --> 00:09:31.270
I believe that we're not appointed

00:09:31.270 --> 00:09:31.280
unto

00:09:31.280 --> 00:09:33.270
wrath, and I believe with all my heart

00:09:33.280 --> 00:09:34.750
that we'll be taken out of here before

00:09:34.760 --> 00:09:36.470
all that mess starts. But it's

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.750
not the beginning of sorrows,

00:09:38.760 --> 00:09:40.230
and I believe we're going to see some

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:42.790
things before the Great

00:09:42.800 --> 00:09:45.510
Tribulation begins.

00:09:45.520 --> 00:09:47.390
That's just me. I believe

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:50.390
some of the other people

00:09:50.400 --> 00:09:52.910
in my circle believe the same way.

00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:54.870
I'm telling you what I

00:09:54.880 --> 00:09:57.070
feel inside my spirit: the beginning, the

00:09:57.080 --> 00:09:59.990
birthing pains. As labor pains upon a

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.070
woman, so will it be. I'm telling you,

00:10:02.080 --> 00:10:03.710
ladies and gentlemen, we're going to see

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:06.750
some stuff. The Lord told me

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:09.030
about what the word was, Braden. I want

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:13.230
to say the exact word.

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:18.150
He said, "I'm putting in my

00:10:21.310 --> 00:10:21.320
closers."And

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:28.550
closers are built for pressure.

00:10:28.560 --> 00:10:30.790
Great pressure is coming.

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:34.390
You must have a sense of urgency.

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:38.950
What's the C-word,

00:10:38.950 --> 00:10:38.960
Braden?

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:41.230
I've said it a thousand times today,

00:10:41.230 --> 00:10:41.240
and

00:10:41.240 --> 00:10:42.710
my mind, when I get on these live streams, just

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:42.720
kind of

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:44.030
goes.

00:10:54.680 --> 00:10:56.310
Obviously, we need to write this

00:10:56.320 --> 00:10:57.670
stuff down when He gives us these words

00:10:57.670 --> 00:10:57.680
because

00:10:57.680 --> 00:10:59.630
it's not our vocabulary.

00:11:00.839 --> 00:11:02.990
So, just knowing that we have to be

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.550
that person with the backbone, with

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:04.560
the

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:06.990
crowbar. I'm trying to tell you all,

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:08.390
the Lord's been

00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:09.630
talking to me outside while I've been

00:11:09.640 --> 00:11:11.150
cleaning and doing the things

00:11:11.160 --> 00:11:13.870
I've been doing. He said, "You must come

00:11:13.880 --> 00:11:17.630
at this stronger, for the great harvest

00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:20.070
of souls is

00:11:20.070 --> 00:11:20.080
ahead.

00:11:20.080 --> 00:11:22.470
For many are called, but few are chosen,

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:25.430
for the harvest is

00:11:25.440 --> 00:11:26.870
plentiful

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:29.470
and the labors are few."That's

00:11:29.470 --> 00:11:29.480
why

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:30.670
I'm

00:11:30.670 --> 00:11:30.680
having

00:11:30.680 --> 00:11:33.630
the urgency of saying,

00:11:33.630 --> 00:11:33.640
Braden,

00:11:33.640 --> 00:11:35.829
having the closer.

00:11:35.839 --> 00:11:37.710
Where we are right now

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:39.030
in this

00:11:39.040 --> 00:11:41.110
dispensation, we're about

00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:43.590
to enter into the dispensation of

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:46.190
judgment, but we're in grace

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:47.870
for just this little bit of a window

00:11:47.880 --> 00:11:51.310
left. Right now, He's calling forth

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:54.750
His church to have some urgency

00:11:54.760 --> 00:11:56.550
to bring in the harvest. That's why

00:11:56.560 --> 00:11:58.870
I was trying to tell you all yesterday,

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:01.070
not that I was knocking

00:12:01.080 --> 00:12:04.270
having a hundred souls born again or

00:12:04.280 --> 00:12:05.910
having

00:12:05.920 --> 00:12:08.710
a few people getting born again, but I

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:10.870
said, "Where is the church having

00:12:10.880 --> 00:12:13.110
major mass

00:12:13.110 --> 00:12:13.120
revival?"The

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:14.790
Lord said to me, "Brandon, I'm

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:17.950
waiting on the souls. I'm leaving the

00:12:17.950 --> 00:12:17.960
ninety-nine

00:12:17.960 --> 00:12:20.670
to go after the

00:12:20.680 --> 00:12:22.430
one."That's

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:24.510
why I was pushing in,

00:12:24.510 --> 00:12:24.520
saying,

00:12:24.520 --> 00:12:26.750
"Lord,

00:12:26.760 --> 00:12:28.350
anoint me with a special anointing,

00:12:28.360 --> 00:12:29.829
whatever it takes to bring in the

00:12:29.839 --> 00:12:32.470
