to the crucifixion

01:39:45.760 --> 01:39:47.150
and the Lord took me out of my body and

01:39:47.160 --> 01:39:49.110
showed me what he went through,

01:39:49.120 --> 01:39:50.990
he told me, 'Brandon,

01:39:51.000 --> 01:39:53.350
what do you not understand? By my

01:39:53.360 --> 01:39:55.430
stripes, you were

01:39:55.430 --> 01:39:55.440
healed.'When

01:39:55.440 --> 01:39:57.710
he showed that to me and

01:39:57.720 --> 01:40:00.310
showed me what he went through,

01:40:00.320 --> 01:40:02.230
Mel Gibson's interpretation of what he

01:40:02.240 --> 01:40:04.190
went through was identical to what I

01:40:04.200 --> 01:40:06.710
saw whenever the Lord took me to

01:40:06.720 --> 01:40:08.230
his crucifixion. He let me see what

01:40:08.240 --> 01:40:13.230
he went through. He said,

01:40:13.240 --> 01:40:16.110
'By my stripes, you're

01:40:16.110 --> 01:40:16.120
healed.'When

01:40:16.120 --> 01:40:20.350
you believe

01:40:20.360 --> 01:40:22.110
in that

01:40:22.120 --> 01:40:26.150
like you did your salvation,

01:40:26.160 --> 01:40:28.350
it's the same faith.

01:40:28.360 --> 01:40:29.910
People don't realize

01:40:34.000 --> 01:40:36.430
how much of a miracle

01:40:36.440 --> 01:40:40.230
it is to say you're born again.

01:40:40.240 --> 01:40:43.110
When he said he took all your sins

01:40:43.120 --> 01:40:45.230
on the cross

01:40:45.240 --> 01:40:48.430
and he became sin for

01:40:48.440 --> 01:40:51.230
you, he also became sickness for you. It

01:40:51.240 --> 01:40:54.830
takes the same amount of faith—faith

01:40:54.830 --> 01:40:54.840
of a

01:40:54.840 --> 01:40:56.070
mustard seed to move a

01:40:56.070 --> 01:40:56.080
mountain.

01:40:56.080 --> 01:40:58.390
But you believe in

01:40:58.400 --> 01:41:00.750
salvation so easily, even

01:41:00.750 --> 01:41:00.760
though

01:41:00.760 --> 01:41:02.910
you can't see it.

01:41:02.920 --> 01:41:05.630
'What can wash away my sin?

01:41:05.640 --> 01:41:09.430
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

01:41:09.440 --> 01:41:14.710
What can make me whole again? Nothing

01:41:14.720 --> 01:41:20.550
but the blood of

01:41:20.550 --> 01:41:20.560
Jesus.'It's

01:41:20.560 --> 01:41:23.190
the same.

01:41:23.200 --> 01:41:25.470
The same blood that washed you white as

01:41:25.480 --> 01:41:27.790
snow from your sin is the same blood

01:41:27.800 --> 01:41:31.510
that washes you and makes you whole.

01:41:31.520 --> 01:41:34.590
Jesus Christ paid

01:41:34.600 --> 01:41:36.350
the price for your sin, sickness,

01:41:36.360 --> 01:41:38.910
disease, poverty, and lack. He paid the

01:41:38.920 --> 01:41:40.910
price for you to walk in victory. And

01:41:40.920 --> 01:41:42.030
that's why he said, 'Brandon, when you

01:41:42.040 --> 01:41:43.550
believe

01:41:43.560 --> 01:41:45.630
in

01:41:45.640 --> 01:41:48.470
healing as much as you do

01:41:48.470 --> 01:41:48.480
salvation...'He

01:41:48.480 --> 01:41:50.950
said, 'Could anybody talk

01:41:50.960 --> 01:41:53.590
you out of

01:41:53.590 --> 01:41:53.600
salvation?'I

01:41:53.600 --> 01:41:55.350
said, 'No, I'd fight them if they

01:41:55.350 --> 01:41:55.360
came

01:41:55.360 --> 01:41:56.870
up to me and said, 'Brandon, you're not

01:41:56.880 --> 01:41:58.510
saved.

01:41:58.520 --> 01:42:00.310
In fact, if you die today, Brandon,

01:42:00.320 --> 01:42:01.590
you're going to hell.'I would fight

01:42:01.590 --> 01:42:01.600
them.'I

01:42:01.600 --> 01:42:04.950
know I'm born again;

01:42:04.960 --> 01:42:07.110
you can't convince me any other

01:42:07.120 --> 01:42:10.310
way. I know that Jesus Christ saved my

01:42:10.320 --> 01:42:12.870
soul. And he said, 'The same way you

01:42:12.880 --> 01:42:14.670
believe that is the same way you need to

01:42:14.680 --> 01:42:17.550
believe in healing.

01:42:17.560 --> 01:42:19.670
The way you believe in salvation is the

01:42:19.680 --> 01:42:21.270
way you need to believe in healing. It takes

01:42:21.280 --> 01:42:26.310
the same

01:42:26.310 --> 01:42:26.320
faith.'Well,

01:42:26.320 --> 01:42:27.870
you're sick and the doctor gives you

01:42:27.880 --> 01:42:30.710
a bad report? No, I believe I'm healed.

01:42:30.720 --> 01:42:34.670
By his stripes, I am healed. He was

01:42:34.680 --> 01:42:36.430
wounded for my

01:42:36.430 --> 01:42:36.440
transgressions,

01:42:36.440 --> 01:42:38.150
he was bruised for my

01:42:38.160 --> 01:42:40.070
iniquities, the chastisement of

01:42:40.070 --> 01:42:40.080
my

01:42:40.080 --> 01:42:43.270
peace was upon him, and with his stripes I

01:42:43.280 --> 01:42:45.990
am healed.

01:42:46.000 --> 01:42:47.670
It's the same faith.

01:42:47.680 --> 01:42:49.910
I believe. And that's when the

01:42:49.920 --> 01:42:51.910
Lord said when you believe it like that

01:42:51.920 --> 01:42:53.590
and you're

01:42:53.590 --> 01:42:53.600
a

01:42:53.600 --> 01:42:55.390
bulldog about it—'I'm fully persuaded

01:42:55.400 --> 01:42:57.550
that I'm healed, I'm fully persuaded

01:42:57.560 --> 01:42:59.310
that I'm

01:42:59.310 --> 01:42:59.320
saved'—he

01:42:59.320 --> 01:43:00.710
said, 'That's where the manifestation

01:43:00.720 --> 01:43:01.590
is.'No

01:43:01.600 --> 01:43:03.070
one can talk you out of your

01:43:03.080 --> 01:43:05.550
salvation. I

01:43:05.550 --> 01:43:05.560
am

01:43:05.560 --> 01:43:09.350
that strong about it;

01:43:09.360 --> 01:43:12.830
you cannot talk me out of it.

01:43:12.840 --> 01:43:14.030
He said the same thing applies. You don't know

01:43:14.040 --> 01:43:16.590
the symptoms of sin.

01:43:16.600 --> 01:43:18.470
Even if you fall down,

01:43:18.470 --> 01:43:18.480
we

01:43:18.480 --> 01:43:19.870
all have sinned and come short of the

01:43:19.880 --> 01:43:21.110
glory of God. That's what he tried to

01:43:21.120 --> 01:43:23.310
show me: 'Brandon, even whenever you

01:43:23.320 --> 01:43:25.670
mess up, you might not

01:43:25.670 --> 01:43:25.680
realize

01:43:25.680 --> 01:43:27.950
the wages of sin is

01:43:27.950 --> 01:43:27.960
death.'But

01:43:27.960 --> 01:43:29.750
you look at all the things that you go

01:43:29.760 --> 01:43:31.110
through in the day—the temptations,

01:43:31.120 --> 01:43:32.590
the thoughts, everything—but you

01:43:32.600 --> 01:43:34.590
still believe regardless of the thoughts

01:43:34.600 --> 01:43:36.470
you have. Regardless of how you

01:43:36.470 --> 01:43:36.480
acted—if

01:43:36.480 --> 01:43:38.030
you say a bad word or do

01:43:38.030 --> 01:43:38.040
whatever—it's

01:43:38.040 --> 01:43:40.270
all sin.

01:43:40.280 --> 01:43:42.750
Sin is sin. There's no sin meter.

01:43:42.750 --> 01:43:42.760
You might say,

01:43:42.760 --> 01:43:44.390
'Well, one sin is greater than

01:43:44.390 --> 01:43:44.400
another

01:43:44.400 --> 01:43:50.710
sin, Brandon.'No, sin is sin,

01:43:50.720 --> 01:43:52.390
but it's all been washed by the blood of

01:43:52.400 --> 01:43:54.390
Jesus. By grace you are

01:43:54.400 --> 01:43:56.670
saved through faith,

01:43:56.680 --> 01:43:58.910
and I receive it. Even if I mess up and

01:43:58.920 --> 01:44:01.470
stub my toe and say a bad word

01:44:01.470 --> 01:44:01.480
or

01:44:01.480 --> 01:44:03.670
something stupid,

01:44:06.480 --> 01:44:08.230
or you think a lustful thought or

01:44:08.240 --> 01:44:11.070
act in anger, it's sin,

01:44:11.080 --> 01:44:13.030
but I still believe I'm saved even if I

01:44:13.040 --> 01:44:14.670
mess up. And that's what he said: 'You

01:44:14.680 --> 01:44:16.110
can't talk yourself out of it.'He said,

01:44:16.120 --> 01:44:17.630
'Do you talk yourself out of it because

01:44:17.630 --> 01:44:17.640
you

01:44:17.640 --> 01:44:18.790
have a symptom?'Well, you're

01:44:18.800 --> 01:44:20.470
overcoming this. You might cough? I'm

01:44:20.480 --> 01:44:24.310
still healed.

01:44:24.320 --> 01:44:25.830
'Well, it doesn't look like you're

01:44:25.840 --> 01:44:27.070
healed, Brother Brandon. You've had a

01:44:27.080 --> 01:44:28.550
snotty nose and a cough for a couple of days, but

01:44:28.560 --> 01:44:29.990
you're still taking communion saying

01:44:30.000 --> 01:44:32.950
you're healed.'Yes, I'm determined. I

01:44:32.960 --> 01:44:34.870
know. I'm fully persuaded. No matter if

01:44:34.880 --> 01:44:36.910
my flesh says it or not,

01:44:36.920 --> 01:44:38.630
I'm healed.

01:44:38.640 --> 01:44:39.870
I might not have the full

01:44:39.880 --> 01:44:41.710
manifestation of the result I'm

01:44:41.720 --> 01:44:45.870
looking for yet, but I'm still healed

01:44:45.880 --> 01:44:47.510
regardless. I'm not moved by what

01:44:47.520 --> 01:44:49.310
I see. I'm not moved by what I feel. I'm

01:44:49.320 --> 01:44:51.190
still healed. Well, you're still

01:44:51.200 --> 01:44:52.830
coughing. Your throat was sore. Well,

01:44:52.840 --> 01:44:55.830
I'm still healed.

01:44:55.840 --> 01:44:57.510
Well, I may have stubbed my toe and said a bad

01:44:57.520 --> 01:45:00.150
word. I'm still saved.

01:45:00.160 --> 01:45:01.630
I may have fallen short.

01:45:01.640 --> 01:45:03.230
The moment I confess it, it's

01:45:03.240 --> 01:45:05.030
washed. Do you understand? It's the same

01:45:05.040 --> 01:45:07.750
thing. But you're fully persuaded

01:45:07.760 --> 01:45:09.070
that you're born again the moment you

01:45:09.080 --> 01:45:10.470
confess it,

01:45:10.480 --> 01:45:12.070
and Jesus lives on the inside of you

01:45:12.080 --> 01:45:14.750
and I'm going to heaven.

01:45:14.760 --> 01:45:20.150
It's the same thing as what he said.

01:45:20.160 --> 01:45:23.910
I'm born again. I'm free. I'm healed.

01:45:23.920 --> 01:45:26.590
I'm fully persuaded. No matter if my

01:45:26.600 --> 01:45:29.030
flesh acts like it or not, even if I

01:45:29.040 --> 01:45:31.350
have a bad attitude and get angry,

01:45:31.360 --> 01:45:33.310
pastor so-and-so or evangelist

01:45:33.320 --> 01:45:36.390
so-and-so, I'm still saved.

01:45:36.400 --> 01:45:38.190
Do you see what I'm starting to tell you? But

01:45:38.200 --> 01:45:43.150
people don't look at it that way.

01:45:43.160 --> 01:45:46.670
I'm still healed.

01:45:46.680 --> 01:45:48.470
I hope I'm helping you because I'm

01:45:48.480 --> 01:45:49.990
telling you it's the same, because the Lord

01:45:50.000 --> 01:45:52.270
said the same amount of faith as it

01:45:52.280 --> 01:45:53.950
takes to be saved is the same amount of

01:45:53.960 --> 01:45:55.750
faith it takes to be healed. You're

01:45:55.760 --> 01:45:59.830
fully persuaded.

01:45:59.840 --> 01:46:05.030
He became poor that I might be rich,

01:46:05.040 --> 01:46:07.150
but I sow my seeds and I believe God

01:46:07.160 --> 01:46:08.190
for a harvest. And that's what he's

01:46:08.200 --> 01:46:09.590
trying to show me is Braden is the

01:46:09.600 --> 01:46:13.110
same.

01:46:13.120 --> 01:46:16.230
I'm not moved by it. Well, you know, I

01:46:16.240 --> 01:46:18.390
got a light bill due and my baby

01:46:18.400 --> 01:46:21.190
needs a new pair of shoes.

01:46:21.200 --> 01:46:23.910
My God is still my provider.

01:46:23.920 --> 01:46:26.110
He'll take care of me.

01:46:26.120 --> 01:46:28.390
I believe it. If he takes care of the

01:46:28.400 --> 01:46:30.150
lilies of the field and the

01:46:30.150 --> 01:46:30.160
sparrows

01:46:30.160 --> 01:46:31.870
of the air, he'll take care of

01:46:31.880 --> 01:46:33.350
me. I've never seen the righteous

01:46:33.360 --> 01:46:35.430
forsaken nor his seed begging bread. I

01:46:35.440 --> 01:46:39.430
believe he's going to take care of me.

01:46:39.440 --> 01:46:41.310
I don't care how he gets it to me. He'll

01:46:41.320 --> 01:46:43.590
take care of me.

01:46:43.600 --> 01:46:47.590
I'm fully persuaded.

01:46:47.600 --> 01:46:48.990
It's the same

01:46:49.000 --> 01:46:51.510
all three.

01:46:51.520 --> 01:46:53.350
It's how you believe in it and how

01:46:53.360 --> 01:46:55.590
you've been taught. Faith comes by

01:46:55.600 --> 01:46:59.190
hearing and hearing by the word of God.

01:46:59.200 --> 01:47:01.430
We take salvation easily because we've heard

01:47:01.440 --> 01:47:03.310
it so much. But there's so much

01:47:03.310 --> 01:47:03.320
resistance

01:47:03.320 --> 01:47:05.190
about prosperity and being

01:47:05.200 --> 01:47:07.630
blessed and healing.

01:47:07.640 --> 01:47:10.710
And you go, 'Well, but Jesus took it all

01:47:10.720 --> 01:47:13.710
for you to walk in victory over it.'Or

01:47:13.710 --> 01:47:13.720
you pray

01:47:13.720 --> 01:47:15.790
a prosperity gospel. I

01:47:15.800 --> 01:47:17.390
like it a lot better than the poverty

01:47:17.400 --> 01:47:21.070
gospel.

01:47:21.080 --> 01:47:22.630
How come you want to cling to poverty so

01:47:22.640 --> 01:47:23.830
much? Does it make you humble?

01:47:26.040 --> 01:47:28.070
The love of money is the root of all

01:47:28.080 --> 01:47:30.230
evil, brother. You can't be blessed.

01:47:30.240 --> 01:47:31.830
Well, I'm going to tell you, if the

01:47:31.840 --> 01:47:33.110
world can have it,

01:47:33.120 --> 01:47:34.390
it rains on the righteous, the

01:47:34.400 --> 01:47:36.270
just and the unjust. Why can't the body

01:47:36.280 --> 01:47:40.030
of Christ have a hold of something?

01:47:40.040 --> 01:47:42.430
He said that he rebukes the devourer

01:47:42.440 --> 01:47:43.950
for your sake and he anoints your

01:47:43.960 --> 01:47:47.070
hands to prosper. Why not?

01:47:47.080 --> 01:47:48.790
I didn't say that you couldn't have

01:47:48.790 --> 01:47:48.800
anything.

01:47:48.800 --> 01:47:49.990
He didn't say we couldn't have

01:47:49.990 --> 01:47:50.000
anything

01:47:50.000 --> 01:47:51.830
as long as it doesn't have you

01:47:51.840 --> 01:47:53.990
and you're not stupid with it.

01:47:54.000 --> 01:47:55.190
And if he tells you to give it away,

01:47:55.200 --> 01:47:59.110
would you give it away?

01:47:59.120 --> 01:48:00.950
Well, I got a brand new Rolex.

01:48:00.960 --> 01:48:02.910
We got it on your wrist. Well,

01:48:02.910 --> 01:48:02.920
Braden,

01:48:02.920 --> 01:48:04.270
I want you to give that to them. I don't

01:48:04.280 --> 01:48:06.830
have one. And say, for instance,

01:48:06.840 --> 01:48:08.709
you got that brand new one on there and he

01:48:08.719 --> 01:48:10.110
says, 'I want you to give it to that man

01:48:10.120 --> 01:48:12.270
over there.'Oh, Lord, I love that watch.

01:48:12.280 --> 01:48:14.350
I can't.

01:48:14.360 --> 01:48:16.030
Do you understand what I'm saying?

01:48:16.040 --> 01:48:17.910
Does it have you? Yes. Here,

01:48:17.920 --> 01:48:21.310
Father. Here you go.

01:48:21.320 --> 01:48:22.510
It's a 'for instance'of what I'm

01:48:22.520 --> 01:48:23.390
trying to say. Well, you got a

01:48:23.400 --> 01:48:25.190
brand new car. It's paid for cash. Here,

01:48:25.200 --> 01:48:27.590
Lord. If he tells you to give it away,

01:48:27.600 --> 01:48:28.990
that's whenever you know that he can

01:48:29.000 --> 01:48:32.030
trust you with it.

01:48:32.040 --> 01:48:33.430
But there's so many people

01:48:33.440 --> 01:48:36.590
that are hung up on things.

01:48:36.600 --> 01:48:38.110
It's a tool.

01:48:38.120 --> 01:48:39.510
Same thing with healings and everything

01:48:39.520 --> 01:48:41.110
else. People get hung up on stuff.

01:48:41.110 --> 01:48:41.120
And

01:48:41.120 --> 01:48:43.070
I just go, it's so simple. We believe

01:48:43.080 --> 01:48:44.030
God for it. And that's what I'm saying.

01:48:44.040 --> 01:48:45.430
Even when my flesh doesn't line up with

01:48:45.440 --> 01:48:46.470
it, I sit there and go, 'Hey, I'm

01:48:46.480 --> 01:48:47.510
healed.

01:48:47.520 --> 01:48:49.430
Either believe it or you don't.

01:48:49.440 --> 01:48:50.910
And either I believe I'm saved or I

01:48:50.910 --> 01:48:50.920
don't.'Even

01:48:50.920 --> 01:48:52.990
if I

01:48:53.000 --> 01:48:59.470
don't act saved for that moment,

01:48:59.480 --> 01:49:00.709
we still believe you're going to heaven

01:49:00.709 --> 01:49:00.719
if you

01:49:00.719 --> 01:49:02.550
die that moment, even after you might

01:49:02.560 --> 01:49:04.830
drop a bad word. You're

01:49:08.640 --> 01:49:10.510
saved, brother, but you just

01:49:10.520 --> 01:49:12.550
said all kinds of things. You were just

01:49:12.560 --> 01:49:14.030
so

01:49:14.040 --> 01:49:15.310
mean.

01:49:15.320 --> 01:49:16.590
That's sin.

01:49:16.600 --> 01:49:20.710
Well, you know, but I'm saved, brother.

01:49:20.720 --> 01:49:22.990
I'm healed, brother.

01:49:23.000 --> 01:49:25.910
I'm delivered, brother. My mind has

01:49:25.920 --> 01:49:28.870
the mind of Christ, brother. I'm not

01:49:28.880 --> 01:49:31.630
moved by what I see. I'm not moved by

01:49:31.640 --> 01:49:33.870
what I feel. I'm moved by what the word

01:49:33.880 --> 01:49:35.750
of God says.

01:49:35.760 --> 01:49:37.910
Hallelujah. Do you believe it? I'm

01:49:37.920 --> 01:49:42.230
delivered

01:49:42.240 --> 01:49:44.030
from PTSD.

01:49:44.030 --> 01:49:44.040
I

01:49:44.040 --> 01:49:46.030
heard somebody right now is

01:49:46.040 --> 01:49:48.070
believing for that. Do you hear me?

01:49:48.080 --> 01:49:50.070
PTSD. You're being delivered from it

01:49:50.080 --> 01:49:52.950
right now.

01:49:52.960 --> 01:49:55.470
You had tragic things happen

01:49:55.480 --> 01:49:58.190
to you.

01:49:58.200 --> 01:49:59.910
These are tragic events and

01:49:59.920 --> 01:50:01.990
it's causing all this

01:50:02.000 --> 01:50:08.270
stuff going on with your mind.

01:50:08.280 --> 01:50:11.230
The Lord is setting you free right now

01:50:11.240 --> 01:50:15.390
from PTSD.

01:50:15.400 --> 01:50:18.030
And it's not just only for war but

01:50:18.040 --> 01:50:20.790
other issues.

01:50:20.800 --> 01:50:22.110
Most people think that has to do

01:50:22.120 --> 01:50:24.190
with war. No, there's

01:50:25.630 --> 01:50:25.640
post-traumatic

01:50:26.560 --> 01:50:28.630
stress disorder of all kinds

01:50:28.640 --> 01:50:31.350
of things.

01:50:31.360 --> 01:50:32.470
Like people who go through law

01:50:32.480 --> 01:50:33.830
enforcement; you have a tragic event

